metadata.name: Ordinary Crystal
metadata.description:
The Extraordinary Crystal has been sold to the highest bidder - they now control the collection.

The Extraordinary Crystal can never leave the winner's wallet - if they sell or transfer the Extraordinary Crystal, a new Ordinary Crystal will instead be minted to the receiving wallet.

In this way, the collector of the Extraordinary Crystal becomes the architect of the collection - will they choose scarcity or abundance?

The Extraordinary Crystals collection is a collaboration from @makeitrad1 and @ktrbychain
